line_1: Again as She grows something stronger,
line_2: And Master's Feet are swath'd no longer,

line_1: When Members knit, and Legs grow stronger,
line_2: Make use of such Machine no longer;

line_1: And tie the Knot much stronger;

line_2: And in Fatigues can hold out longer;

line_1: But, without any Doubt, I shall find myself stronger,
line_2: When I've took the same Physic a Week or two longer.
